Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.86,0:06:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就以上四种吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.87,0:06:57.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  真的假的！！
