Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.53,0:07:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古文5
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.08,0:07:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界史4
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.69,0:07:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本史5
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.44,0:07:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,数学Ⅱ5
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.00,0:07:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理科5
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.53,0:07:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外语5
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.17,0:07:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,体育5
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.74,0:07:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艺术5
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.52,0:07:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么有一个是4啊  真难过
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.46,0:07:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不如全4呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.83,0:07:14.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  老师从山里回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.23,0:07:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正到哪都会被通知  不如一次知道个够…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.95,0:07:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位太太  我有事相问
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.37,0:07:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道宇宙的真理！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.72,0:07:28.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真想知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.65,0:07:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.83,0:07:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深处究竟有些什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.15,0:07:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  这就是宇宙的真理
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.22,0:07:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这！  这就是宇宙的真理！？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.51,0:07:54.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不该知道啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.83,0:07:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住宅区的太太居然知道宇宙的真理！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.26,0:08:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！  希望有一天我也能够像那位太太那样知晓一切
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.42,0:08:07.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想成为知晓卖剩宠物的去向的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.81,0:08:12.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  无论好坏  我都不想知道自己的未来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.14,0:08:15.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就买下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.12,0:08:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糸色先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.66,0:08:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.12,0:08:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亏我还带来了上次约好的土豆炖肉
