Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.02,0:08:32.75,zhushi1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-90\pos(500,100)}春眠不觉晓
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.40,0:08:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.01,0:08:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次是做梦结局
