Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.09,0:09:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦中的我备受瞩目哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.56,0:09:47.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是臼井同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.22,0:09:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是臼井同学！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.35,0:09:49.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是臼井同学哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.78,0:09:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.89,0:09:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臼井同学  迷人的发型有点乱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.43,0:09:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢了  木村同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.07,0:09:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！  卡爱拉你好诈哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.71,0:09:59.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好诈哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.57,0:10:01.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然对我们的臼井同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.34,0:10:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥米！  梦里的臼井同学大受欢迎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.54,0:10:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.46,0:10:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一群白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.23,0:10:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,区区配角有什么资格做梦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.79,0:10:13.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎么渲染自己  配角始终是配角
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.81,0:10:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中途观看的人错以为这是流氓打斗动画谁负责
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.61,0:10:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我搞清楚状况  然后哪凉快待哪去！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.11,0:10:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这{\fs35}秃子{\r}！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.11,0:10:20.93,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[真是斎藤千和…]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.01,0:10:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说个不停的音无同学！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.81,0:10:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  四眼田鸡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.21,0:10:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁想看你梦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.94,0:10:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真打算展示给人看  就给老娘做个像样点的梦！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.05,0:10:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,单…单纯的毒舌！？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.50,0:10:35.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.88,0:10:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.07,0:10:38.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扣杀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.07,0:10:38.01,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[小森雾的对手为「アタックNo.1」（Attack No.1／排球女将）的主角鲇原梢]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.02,0:10:40.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.87,0:10:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来轮到我了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.09,0:10:43.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在外面玩的小森同学！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.06,0:10:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春～天～天～天～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.41,0:10:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三只小鸟袭击猫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.01,0:10:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三个人活埋村长
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.11,0:10:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不普通的普通少女！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.89,0:10:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙一点不普通！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.23,0:10:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普通的！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.59,0:10:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很普通的！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.23,0:11:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的很普通的！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.37,0:11:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算这是梦  你们也太自由发挥了吧！！
