Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.24,0:19:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你居然和父母说那种事！？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.14,0:19:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有  谁和你有恋情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.78,0:19:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  这也算瞒父母？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.81,0:19:21.85,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父母并不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.08,0:19:23.43,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…我的出生时间
